{"slug":"navy-jko","title":"Navy Jko","bucket":"cbt_jko","source_filename":"Navy Jko.docx","kind":"qa","question_count":75,"word_count":566,"qas":[{"q":"Konnichiwa こんにちは","a":"Hello (formal-informal greeting)"},{"q":"Ohayoo\nおはよう","a":"Good morning (informal)"},{"q":"Ohayoo gozaimas\nおはようございます。","a":"Good morning (formal)"},{"q":"Hajimemashite\nはじめまして","a":"Nice to meet you"},{"q":"Konbanwa\nこんばんは","a":"Good evening"},{"q":"Oyasumi\nおやすみ","a":"good night (informal)"},{"q":"Oyasuminasai\nおやすみなさい","a":"Good night (formal)"},{"q":"Tanaka desu. Doozo yoroshiku.","a":"My name is Tanaka. Remember me well."},{"q":"Nihon wa doo desu ka.","a":"How do you like Japan?"},{"q":"Watashi wa Jon desu. Kochira koso doozo yoroshiku.","a":"My name is John. Remember me well."},{"q":"Nihon e yookoso.","a":"Welcome to Japan (formal)."},{"q":"Yookoso irasshaimashita.","a":"Welcome to our home (formal)"},{"q":"Ii desu ne.","a":"It is good."},{"q":"Mata ato de.","a":"See you later."},{"q":"Mata ashita\nまたあした","a":"See you tomorrow."},{"q":"Arigatoo","a":"Thank you"},{"q":"Doomo arigatoo gozaimasu.","a":"Thank you very much"},{"q":"Doo itashimashite","a":"You're welcome."},{"q":"Doozo goenryonaku meshigatte kudasai.","a":"Enjoy your meal, don't be shy."},{"q":"shitsureishimasu\nしつれいします","a":"Excuse me. (Pardon me.)"},{"q":"Gomennasai\nごめんなさい","a":"I'm sorry."},{"q":"~ shite mo ii desu ka.","a":"Allow me to ..."},{"q":"Kore wa purezento desu.","a":"This is for you."},{"q":"Doozo uketori kudasai.","a":"Please, accept it, it's yours."},{"q":"Soko made shinakute mo yakatta noni.","a":"You shouldn't have."},{"q":"Kekkoo desu","a":"No, thank you."},{"q":"Haitte mo ii desu ka.","a":"May I enter?"},{"q":"Doozo ohairi kudasai","a":"Please come in."},{"q":"Haitte wa ikemasen","a":"No, you may not enter."},{"q":"Matte kudasai.","a":"Please wait."},{"q":"Hai","a":"Yes"},{"q":"Iie","a":"No."},{"q":"Ii desu","a":"OK."},{"q":"Tabun","a":"Maybe."},{"q":"Daijoobu desu ka.","a":"Is everything OK?"},{"q":"Ii desu ka.","a":"Are you ready?"},{"q":"Chotto matte kudasai.","a":"One moment, please."},{"q":"Kore wa tadashii desu ka.","a":"Is this right?"},{"q":"Iie chigaimasu.","a":"No, that's wrong."},{"q":"Kono hito wa dare desu ka.","a":"Who is this man?"},{"q":"Kono onna no hito wa dare desu ka.","a":"Who is this woman?"},{"q":"Kono Kodomosan wa anata no okosan desu ka.","a":"Is this your child?"},{"q":"Tashika desu ka.","a":"Are you sure?"},{"q":"~ ga arimasu ka.","a":"Do you have ... ?"},{"q":"Hai, ikutsuka arimasu.","a":"Yes, I have some."},{"q":"Kono tabemono wa atarashii desu ka.","a":"Is the food fresh"},{"q":"Kono tabemono wa itande imasu.","a":"This food is spoiled"},{"q":"kore wa butaniku desu ka, soretomo gyuuniku desu ka.","a":"Is this pork or beef?"},{"q":"Gyuuniku desu.","a":"This is beef"},{"q":"Kore wa donna kudamono desu ka.","a":"What kind of fruit is this?"},{"q":"kore wa ringo desu.","a":"This is an apple"},{"q":"Motto ikaga desu ka.","a":"Would you like some more?"},{"q":"kekkoo desu. Moo onaka ga ippai desu.","a":"No, thank you, I am full."},{"q":"gochisoo sama deshita. Totemo oishikatta desu","a":"Thank you, the food was very good."},{"q":"Ocha o doozo.","a":"Have some tea."},{"q":"Kono mizu wa nonde mo daijoobu desu ka.","a":"Is this water safe to drink?"},{"q":"Mizu wa ichi do wakashita hoga ii desu.","a":"It's better to boil the water once."},{"q":"Inryoosui ga hitsuyoo desu.","a":"We need potable water."},{"q":"Te wa doko de araemasu ka.","a":"Where can I wash my hands?"},{"q":"Toire wa doko desu ka.","a":"Where is the latrine?"},{"q":"eigo o hanashimasu ka.","a":"Do you speak English"},{"q":"Eigo wa hanashimasen.","a":"I don't speak English."},{"q":"Dare ka eigo o hanasu hito ga imasu ka.","a":"Does anyone here speak English?"},{"q":"Watashi wa Nihongo ga hanasemasen.","a":"I don't speak Japanese."},{"q":"Nanigo o hanashimasu ka.","a":"What language do you speak?"},{"q":"Nihongo o hanashimasu.","a":"I speak Japanese."},{"q":"Kankokugo o hanashimasu.","a":"I speak Korean"},{"q":"Wakarimasu ka.","a":"Do you understand?"},{"q":"Wakarimasen.","a":"I don't understand."},{"q":"Yukkuri hanashite kudasai","a":"Please speak slowly."},{"q":"Kurikaeshite kudasai","a":"Please repeat."},{"q":"Tsuuyaku ga irimasu","a":"I need an interpreter."},{"q":"Tsuuyaku no hito ga kimasu","a":"The interpreter is coming."},{"q":"Tsuuyaku no hito wa doko desu ka.","a":"Where is the interpreter?"},{"q":"Moo ichido itte kudasai","a":"Please say it again."}],"prose":null}